.TH "alarm_timer_arm" 9 "alarm_timer_arm" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
alarm_timer_arm \- Posix timer callback to arm a timer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" alarm_timer_arm
.BI "(struct k_itimer *timr "  ","
.BI "ktime_t expires "  ","
.BI "bool absolute "  ","
.BI "bool sigev_none "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "timr" 12
Pointer to the posixtimer data struct
.IP "expires" 12
The new expiry time
.IP "absolute" 12
Expiry value is absolute time
.IP "sigev_none" 12
Posix timer does not deliver signals
